Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你下來 聽不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的床
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 是誰把它放進來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上校麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 不能再往下想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在最重要的是找到代替安妮莫奈的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's All In The Mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要讓我等到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方有巨大的積雨雲 管制塔還沒下達著陸許可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們進入瓦爾薩瓦領空已經多長時間了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有急事的話可以像以往那樣使用小型高速艇降落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向管制塔要求著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲間出現了縫隙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底要在這裡呆到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們明明知道不抓緊時間是要出大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你現在需要休息 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在事態惡化之前盡我的全部所能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:04:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以塔爾荷 讓我…去……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說我更覺得過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種沒有設置限能裝置的LFO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要駕駛員使用強化神經系統的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及乘坐後強制促進睡眠的兩種藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人型機動武器黎明時期的負面遺產 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本應該是被封存解體的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說多少參與了開發的我們不好這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們必須擊落AFX 這也是事實對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這樣下去霍蘭德會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但我也不能阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到迎來那最後一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得再往前走就不安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回到剛才那眼泉的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都累了吧 是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坐得屁股都疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽見了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看前邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內戰結束已經十年了 竟然還是這樣的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以忍受不幸的人民化為難民 往別的州遷移
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是沒落的塔州的最終結果麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米尼克上尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原情報部的人竟然說得出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是艦長的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡他失去了妻子和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 你干什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 開車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為就你在戰爭中失去了親人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的不是只有你一個人 不是只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別歎氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們現在在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們一輩子也離不開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會有辦法的 我們以前不也克服了各種困難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢 現在跟以前能一樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫裡斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德不在 塔爾荷也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾德 斯特納…全都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也一直沒精神 你還在這裡瞎扯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到吃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊樹上還有好多呢 我們一起去摘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫裡斯也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 莫裡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就開門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是多米尼克特務上尉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是諾瓦克財團的迪卡德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦克? 上校的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是在哪裡見過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初送那個過去的時候確實見過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們就是安妮莫奈的下任候補?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人還剛被送來不久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 只靠這座城市的話獻體是遠遠不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您應該知道這座城市的別名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦爾薩瓦 別稱Joy Division
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想曾生活在這裡的你們應該明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個安妮莫奈在等著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就待在這不好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼怪 優萊卡 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我有什麼意見你倒是直說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不要走 你這樣孩子們也很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把我們送到這裡 我能理解你的焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是正因為如此我們才應該冷靜地行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以優萊卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這些是安妮莫奈…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還滿意麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的設計技術比起上次要進步多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是骨骼 通過把面部肌肉的活動控制在最小程度上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得它們更為接近真品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 他們要干什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐性檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過程度還比不上安妮莫奈完成的那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是因為杜伊大人要求迅速準備三個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始投藥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然上次那個是特殊情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐藥性強 對通道的依賴程度也相當高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過投放興奮作用強烈的藥物 可以一時間把它拉回現實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個意義上 它也是相當特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括它被發現在這城市這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮莫奈 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜伊大人的命令是請您在三個當中選出一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您覺得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 實驗剛剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有能夠替代安妮莫奈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在戰爭中失去了親人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我比誰都清楚孤獨一人的艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想幫助她 幫助安妮莫奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我明知道藥物會侵蝕她的身體和精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:18:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可為了滿足她 我…我就……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為找到了她的後繼 就可以把她從現在的生活中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果為此就要選擇其他的人來承受同樣的命運 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面寫的是真相麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗體科拉利安的出現 物理宇宙的崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都事先就包括在上校的計劃中麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明知會把無辜的人民捲入的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 好沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德說有什麼萬一的話就用它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德 我打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫裡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們待在這別動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫裡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫裡斯…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦總指揮部發來命令 要我們立即前往特雷澤阿技研
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去特雷澤阿?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 據說在其內部藏匿有月光州的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 命令我們和第18獨立連隊匯合後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速逮捕月光州全體成員及特雷澤阿的全體研究員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去特雷澤阿的路上有沒有可以補給武器彈藥的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您三思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全體乘員 本艦現在前往特雷澤阿技研 請迅速各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍 本艦現在前往特雷澤阿技研 請迅速各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮莫奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從過去的事實前往未知的真實的少年少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地分割的世界之間靠著一種感情連在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Don't You Want Me?


